--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-12-07)
F: Add support for CentOS 7

* Version 0.3.1 (2020-11-27)
E: Improve Monit configuration file

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-11-23)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (rsyslog_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-11-09)
B: Load module 'imfile' by default

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-11-09)
C: Redesign config syntax (rsyslog_config_(all|group|host))
B: Fix parameters rsyslog_config_group, rsyslog_config_host

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-11-06)
F: Initial release
